 	function Poly_Prim = POLY_PRIM(Poly)		% 	Computes the derivative of a polynomial, P, with 	%	the highest power first.    	% Toolbox for DIGITAL FILTERS USING MATLAB 		% 	Author: 		Lars Wanhammar, 2002-07-23    % 	Modified by:	LW 2007-07-23	% 	Copyright:		by authors - not released for commercial use	% 	Version: 		1		% 	Known bugs:		 	% 	Report bugs to:	Wanhammar@gmail.com		N = length(Poly);		for j = 1:N-1		Poly_Prim(j) = (N-j)*Poly(j);	end